        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">TL;DR</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Client management requires tracking communication history, contracts, payments, and ongoing relationships with buyers. Scattered emails and text messages fail. A proper system keeps all buyer information organized with a visual sales pipeline, lead scoring, and analytics—so you know exactly where every buyer stands and who needs attention.
        </p>
      </aside>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        Your reputation depends on client relationships. Poor communication, lost contracts, forgotten follow-ups—these destroy trust. This page explains how professional breeders manage clients without drowning in disorganized messages.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: Why Breeders Search for This -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
